 />\n黃泉月露娜：鵜殿麻由<br />\n五十嵐清華：福原綾香<br />\n桃喰綺羅莉：沢城みゆき<br />\n<br />\n直播link(香港時間21:00) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://vaughnlive.tv/sherming88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvaughnlive.tv%2Fsherming88&d=8WwZ2LD91TkRcLKoFnA1pE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=82750625\" target=\"_blank\">https://vaughnlive.tv/sherming88</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-42683-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-42683-1-1.html&d=8WwZ2LD91TkRcLKoFnA1pE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f84e7c74\" target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-42683-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"bf669625b8ccab2198316c79aabf4c275ad335ea","tid":365582,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8306d50cb3133f31e20d3a44fa5ea1f52337c3","tid":365582,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:08:32.000Z","msg":"入兩發彈個到唔係好明，即係點解？"},{"pid":"148d789b17a50eeaf79e921aa64c09eb595da5b3","tid":365582,"uid":58968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:18:24.000Z","msg":"地獄少女大個左就變職業賭徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7105b422a0dba5f1a2afe36595cbea1b1f8d69b0","tid":365582,"uid":70375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入兩發彈個到唔係好明，即係點解？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為一局最多可以開五槍（一個錯哂 一個啱哂）<br />\n所以痴線婆心諗如果入咗兩飛<br />\n夢子按常理應該會全中<br />\n而自己鳩撞搏錯哂或者中一兩題<br />\n等自己比夢子射<br />\n最終目標係自爆<br />\n實際上係自己同自己玩俄羅斯輪盤<br />\n所以夢子見兩飛彈就知道痴線婆特登玩野"},{"pid":"38507214d9930e8d6537ee6224e51d30433551af","tid":365582,"uid":70375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:58:41.000Z","msg":"臨